        {
            "title": "警旺角搗製毒工場 檢大麻毒品值88萬 兩男涉販毒落網",
            "description": "<div class=\"video paragraphs medium\">\n<p> <figure class=\"margin-top-1\">\n<img alt=\"兩名被捕男子帶署調查。\" class=\"size-full w-100\" src=\"https://image.stheadline.com/f/680p0/0x0/100/none/266731539c8548457ff91d7d82e874bc/stheadline/inewsmedia/20250510/_2025051012170785514.jpg\"/>\n<figcaption class=\"caption-text\">兩名被捕男子帶署調查。</figcaption>\n</figure>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner1\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner1-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n<p>將軍澳警區特別職務隊人員根據線報及經深入調查後，昨日（9日）下午在旺角砵蘭街搗破一個懷疑製毒工場。行動中，人員突擊搜查上址一住宅單位，並在該單位內檢獲共約2.5公斤懷疑大麻草、3.7公斤懷疑大麻油、314支懷疑大麻油煙彈、260克懷疑大麻糖、200克懷疑大麻餅，以及一批懷疑用作製造大麻油煙彈的材料及工具。行動中檢獲的毒品總市值約88萬元。\n\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4240594/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"行動中檢獲的證物。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/4b37777a30def4c0d18e856d8e1a281f/2025-05/TKO_SDS_1.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        行動中檢獲的證物。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n</p>\n<p>該單位內兩名分別30歲及31歲本地男子涉嫌「製造危險藥物」及「販運危險藥物」被捕，兩名被捕人現正被扣留調查。<br/>\n <br/>\n警方重申，製造及販運危險藥物為嚴重罪行，根據香港法例第134章《危險藥物條例》，最高可被判終身監禁和罰款五百萬元。警方呼籲市民切勿以身試法。\n\n\n\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner2\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner2-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://std.stheadline.com/realtime/article/2068222/即時-港聞-警旺角搗製毒工場-檢大麻毒品值88萬-兩男涉販毒落網",
            "pub_date": "2025-05-10 12:22:31",
            "source": "stheadline",
            "kind": 1,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "西安UFO｜雷雨夜再現「飛龍」 有人稱聽到「龍吟聲」｜有片",
            "description": "<div class=\"video paragraphs medium\">\n<div id=\"vdo-player-container\">\n<video class=\"video-js vjs-default-skin\" controls=\"\" id=\"vdo-player\" muted=\"\" playsinline=\"\" poster=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/686e386/0x0/100/none/d67b6f6554ecf0aaa239148f6bce879c/2025-05/Clipboard10_1.png\" width=\"100%\">\n<source src=\"https://video.hkhl.hk/1064b08f2d5471f0bff14177d1c00102/c4625a3d6c5d4292868dbca0cc239f34-058fb7ccd7d7bcb014affd7c760147b8-ld.mp4\" type=\"video/mp4\">\n                        Your browser does not support the video tag.\n                    </source></video>\n<div class=\"vdo-ad-container web\" data-vslot=\"vod_ad\" id=\"div-gpt-vad-681ed31c39471\"></div>\n<div class=\"vdo-ad-container mweb\" data-vslot0=\"vod_ad,2\" id=\"div-gpt-vad-681ed31c39472\"></div>\n</div>\n<p> <figure class=\"margin-top-1\">\n<img alt=\"西安雷雨夜再現「飛龍」， 有人稱聽到「龍吟聲」。\" class=\"size-full w-100\" src=\"https://image.stheadline.com/f/680p0/0x0/100/none/ccda086e20cfb0aa6ef2ba01d384a07d/stheadline/inewsmedia/20250510/_2025051012133368731.jpg\"/>\n<figcaption class=\"caption-text\">西安雷雨夜再現「飛龍」， 有人稱聽到「龍吟聲」。</figcaption>\n</figure>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner1\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner1-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n<p>西安8日晚突遭短暫暴雨，雷暴交加中，多名市民在夜空中再次捕捉到神秘黑影「龍形」不明飛行物。有網友更稱聽到老牛般的咆哮聲類似「龍吟」。\n\n</p>\n<p><strong>相關新聞：<a href=\"https://www.stheadline.com/realtime-china/3452576/\">西安UFO？︱雷雨夜半空現「飛龍」 官方：無法解釋︱有片</a></strong>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"西安雷雨夜再現「飛龍」。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/31170c50cf149d2ba435b5bf0c901b1e/2025-05/vlcsnap-2025-05-10-11h37m37s991.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        西安雷雨夜再現「飛龍」。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"當地網民留言。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/5dc2a16b122aba7921ec6e8e204949bb/2025-05/1_2_16.png\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        當地網民留言。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"當地網民留言。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/20cb351b50f4584f3a77b130bd76b7a7/2025-05/2_17.png\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        當地網民留言。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"當地網民留言。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/a73922de4f3c6b3f81e7984a8f136650/2025-05/3_15.png\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        當地網民留言。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"市民拍下西安天空有黑影飛過。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/861d0ec2e9ae00a1c4cf6ff64da602db/2025-05/vlcsnap-2025-05-10-11h37m45s550.png\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        市民拍下西安天空有黑影飛過。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"市民拍下西安天空有黑影飛過，忽然90度向下「飛」。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/7e10efe0aeef300ba8b7a6f1c53e70c6/2025-05/vlcsnap-2025-05-10-11h37m49s700.png\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        市民拍下西安天空有黑影飛過，忽然90度向下「飛」。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n</p>\n<p>此前，5月2日西安雷雨夜空已曾經出現條狀不明物，多名網友拍到黑影疾速掠過夜空，有目擊者稱不像是風箏和鳥類，「像龍一樣圍著盤旋，至少有三條。」\n\n</p>\n<p>當時西安市氣象局工作人員表示，她也看到了不明飛行物的視頻，有網友稱形狀像龍，也有網友稱像塑料袋在空中飛舞。2號西安確實有過雷雨天，屬於這個季節的正常現象，沒有監測到異常狀況，無法解釋，可咨詢一下西安市氣象台。西安市氣象台工作人員表示還沒聽說不明飛行物的事。\n\n\n\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner2\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner2-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>",
