            "title": "周末睇波手冊│周日晚有西甲國家打吡 英超爭4大戰紐卡素對車路士 母親節黃金時間免費直播",
            "description": "<div class=\"video paragraphs medium\">\n<p> <figure class=\"margin-top-1\">\n<img alt=\"周日晚有西甲國家打吡，英超爭4大戰紐卡素對車路士。路透社\" class=\"size-full w-100\" src=\"https://image.stheadline.com/f/680p0/0x0/100/none/c825f2f0d50f75e07577a4049f2cb264/stheadline/inewsmedia/20250509/_2025051001051182575.jpg\"/>\n<figcaption class=\"caption-text\">周日晚有西甲國家打吡，英超爭4大戰紐卡素對車路士。路透社</figcaption>\n</figure>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner1\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner1-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n<p>隨住英超、德甲和法甲的冠軍爭奪戰已經結束，大家的焦點落在西甲和意甲身上。周日晚上10時15分，西甲就上演榜首巴塞隆拿主場對次席皇家馬德里的大戰，雙方目前相差4分，勝負直接影響爭標形勢，這場國家打吡球迷當然不可錯過。\n\n</p><h2>西甲國家打吡直接影響爭標形勢</h2>\n<p>再者雙方日前於西班牙盃決賽碰頭，彼此已鬥得十分激烈，巴塞加時後擊敗皇馬捧盃，今季各賽事3次鬥後者全勝，銀河艦隊今仗肯定想報仇，大戰氣氛更濃。值得留意，周日還有荷甲國家打吡，飛燕諾主場鬥燕豪芬，前者雖然已沒有爭冠希望，但如果在今仗擊敗死敵，就大有機會打擊後者的衛冕夢，肯定不會手下留情。\n\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"巴塞隆拿於4月尾，在西班牙盃決賽擊敗皇馬捧盃。路透社\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/f54fda21a3b7772a1c1b959db639de59/2025-05/1_23.JPG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        巴塞隆拿於4月尾，在西班牙盃決賽擊敗皇馬捧盃。路透社\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"巴塞今季在各賽事3次對皇馬全勝。路透社\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/0adc86836d0eeba24ed847ef09837cc4/2025-05/2_0_5.JPG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        巴塞今季在各賽事3次對皇馬全勝。路透社\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"皇馬今季對巴室全敗。路透社\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/34e048d4d078c3b4d1ba887d47ae4985/2025-05/3_20.JPG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        皇馬今季對巴室全敗。路透社\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"皇馬如果想保持西甲爭標希望，今場國家打吡不容有失。路透社\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/d0b7890179b7da06a61a72f9971ea882/2025-05/4_17.JPG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        皇馬如果想保持西甲爭標希望，今場國家打吡不容有失。路透社\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"皇馬今仗非勝不可。路透社\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/c41d414ce6393c728d11b830550e32f2/2025-05/5_13.JPG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        皇馬今仗非勝不可。路透社\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n</p><h2>麥湯文尼會否再做拿玻里爭冠救兵？</h2>\n<p>意甲方面，拿玻里完成35輪後高踞榜首，目前有3分的領先優勢，餘下3輪全勝就肯定奪冠。他們在周日深夜2時45分主場對下游的熱拿亞，陣中曼聯棄將麥湯文尼會否再次成為贏波功臣，到時在HOY76台搵答案。\n\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"拿玻里餘下3輪全勝，肯定可以封王。路透社\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/ce990d37acbdcf6d28b2d865cac5e0cb/2025-05/1_24.JPG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        拿玻里餘下3輪全勝，肯定可以封王。路透社\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"麥湯文尼今季多次以入球拯救拿玻里。路透社\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/75556b5c91b55a66000450ca98e6e3d5/2025-05/2_16.JPG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        麥湯文尼今季多次以入球拯救拿玻里。路透社\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"麥湯文尼最近腳風大順。路透社\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/08cdcbc46c8a809525fee5ceeb2c28bd/2025-05/3_21.JPG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        麥湯文尼最近腳風大順。路透社\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"麥湯文尼會否再做拿玻里的贏波英雄？路透社\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/864d728d10c5094af61d3c0f683e7972/2025-05/4_18.JPG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        麥湯文尼會否再做拿玻里的贏波英雄？路透社\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n</p><h2>英超歐聯席位之爭好激烈</h2>\n<p>英超的冠軍和降班之爭已經確定，焦點就轉移在歐聯席位爭奪戰，前5名有得踢，除冠軍利物浦已鎖定一席，2至7位的阿仙奴、曼城、紐卡素、車路士、諾定咸森林和阿士東維拉爭餘下4個名額，有2隊無份。\n\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"紐卡素與爭歐聯席位的直接競爭對手車路士正面交鋒。路透社\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/c0d3193a9cc0ef494f2dc5ecc972b5e3/2025-05/1_25.JPG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        紐卡素與爭歐聯席位的直接競爭對手車路士正面交鋒。路透社\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"紐卡素近3輪英超收錄勝和負各一。路透社\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/4f1edec6557d4560f1b3ee54aa035654/2025-05/2_17.JPG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        紐卡素近3輪英超收錄勝和負各一。路透社\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"今場紐卡素對車路士的前列大戰，安排在周日旳上7時正的黃金時間進行。路透社\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/e175f3aebdddba6a61bd1f548548b70d/2025-05/3_22.JPG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        今場紐卡素對車路士的前列大戰，安排在周日旳上7時正的黃金時間進行。路透社\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"紐車大戰在Viu96台免費直播。路透社\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/2dad6d0d330613955c8ea2a870169bf6/2025-05/4_19.JPG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        紐車大戰在Viu96台免費直播。路透社\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"車路士剛周中在歐協聯躋身決賽。路透社\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/a6e7e26bd961a4f24c153591e312a5d0/2025-05/5_14.JPG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        車路士剛周中在歐協聯躋身決賽。路透社\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"車路士目前於英超排第5位。路透社\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/cb30665b14f51a40f7701a8a82242392/2025-05/6_8.JPG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        車路士目前於英超排第5位。路透社\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n</p><h2>周日晚上7:00 紐車大戰Viu96台免費播</h2>\n<p>第4位的紐卡素，周日晚上7點就會在主場對第5名的車路士，兩支同得63分的球隊直接交鋒，本身已極具瞄頭。這場在母親節黃金時間上演的大戰，在Viu96台免費直播，球迷當然不可錯過。而晚上11時30分，還有利物浦對阿仙奴的榜首大戰，剛在歐聯4強出局的槍手，今場如果再輸，隨時連亞軍席位不保，甚至歐聯席位都有危機，今仗肯定會搏老命﹗\n\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"阿仙奴剛在歐聯4強出局。路透社\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/15039ffb25137eb616ae88b29af05ba6/2025-05/1_26.JPG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        阿仙奴剛在歐聯4強出局。路透社\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"阿仙奴球員要收拾心情，準備鬥利物浦。路透社\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/f400621ce929d3e3b20ac9c3fd4da71d/2025-05/2_18.JPG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        阿仙奴球員要收拾心情，準備鬥利物浦。路透社\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"阿仙奴目前於英超排第2，但仍未鎖定歐聯席位。路透社\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/ad39bf6e031377f64b15b83bf003c2d0/2025-05/3_23.JPG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        阿仙奴目前於英超排第2，但仍未鎖定歐聯席位。路透社\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"利物浦提早封王後，上輪即不敵車路士。路透社\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/ec415d324712a855cdae048fd55d7da2/2025-05/4_20.JPG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        利物浦提早封王後，上輪即不敵車路士。路透社\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"利物浦將會硬撼阿仙奴。路透社\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/faae0e7bdd7c6e314a1d491b64c3518b/2025-05/5_15.JPG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        利物浦將會硬撼阿仙奴。路透社\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"阿仙奴今場賽前要列隊歡迎新科英超冠軍利物浦。路透社\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/e0050fc38ee115c9f9293a558739400f/2025-05/6_9.JPG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        阿仙奴今場賽前要列隊歡迎新科英超冠軍利物浦。路透社\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n</p>\n<p><strong>本周末精選直播賽事<br/>\n周六<br/>\n<em>開賽時間(香港時間)    賽事    對賽    直播</em></strong><br/>\n晚上10:00    英超    修咸頓 對 曼城    Now621台<br/>\n深夜0:00    意甲    拉素 對 祖雲達斯    HOY77台<br/>\n深夜0:30    英超    般尼茅夫 對 阿士東維拉    Now621、611台<br/>\n深夜0:30    德甲    拜仁慕尼黑 對 慕遜加柏    Now639台<br/>\n深夜3:00    西甲    馬德里體育會 對 皇家蘇斯達    Now632台\n\n</p>\n<p><strong>周日<br/>\n<em>開賽時間(香港時間)    賽事    對賽    直播</em></strong><br/>\n晚上7:00    英超    紐卡素 對 車路士    Now6